{"tid":1795554,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日聖誕有場中國球隊大戰香港球隊嘅波 大家唔係唔入場呀嘛","createTime":"2019-12-24T03:59:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T04:09:10.000Z","uid":281918,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"adfcf06d6a166f325dcae86a90f6e06f14cb9e2f","tid":1795554,"uid":281918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:59:02.000Z","msg":"冇錯 就係用<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5000萬班費嘅廣州畜力</span></strong>vs東方龍獅<br />\n唔可以比廣州畜力贏到任何一個香港聯賽體系嘅冠軍<br />\n唔可以比佢代表香港參加亞洲賽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0nBb32d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0nBb32d.jpg&h=093f5f3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊入旺角場狙擊佢啦<br />\n<br />\n港超聯應叫港超，關廣州L事<br />\n香港人撐香港ball 基本盤<br />\n<br />\n幫手推到紅旗，ok？"},{"pid":"240b4635d8c8e60ce0aefe280483ea6534404923","tid":1795554,"uid":281918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:02:13.000Z","msg":"光復香港由港足做起<br />\n<br />\nWe are Hong Kong 🇭🇰🇭🇰<br />\nOle ole ole<br />\n<br />\n本谷旨在有興趣睇港足港超或者有睇開的球迷入嚟討論波經。以老帶新，由資深球迷帶新手球迷入門，交換資訊，降低香港睇波門檻，等愈來愈多球迷入場撐港足，重建香港球巿<br />\n<br />\n光復香港由重建港足文化開始<br />\nTg: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpoLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=13f2ddbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ</a><br />\n<br />\nIg: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B6WJbUjnBHP/?igshid=1isl7odu4ze6x\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB6WJbUjnBHP%2F%3Figshid%3D1isl7odu4ze6x&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpoLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=e8ddc6f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB6WJbUjnBHP%2F%3Figshid%3D1isl7odu4ze6x&h=2d6889f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B6WJbUjnBHP/?igshid=1isl7odu4ze6x</a>"},{"pid":"3087039479b18c0f2a2c858